SUMMARY: TINA – The Tina Turner Musical
DESCRIPTION:An uplifting comeback story like no other\, TINA – The Tina T
 urner Musical is the inspiring journey of a woman who broke barriers and 
 became the Queen of Rock n’ Roll. Set to the pulse-pounding soundtrack of
  her most beloved hits\, this electrifying sensation will send you soarin
 g to the rafters.\n\nOne of the world’s best-selling artists of all time\
 , Tina Turner won 12 Grammy Awards and her live shows were seen by millio
 ns\, with more concert tickets sold than any other solo performer in musi
 c history.\n\nFeaturing her much loved songs\, TINA – The Tina Turner Mus
 ical is written by Pulitzer Prize-winning playwright Katori Hall.
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,Live,Theatre,Tickets
