 he Jets\, Tiny Dancer and Crocodile Rock to deeper cuts like Funeral for 
 a Friend\, Madman Across the Water\, All the Girls Love Alice\, Mona Lisa
 s & Mad Hatters and many\, many more. No tracks. No tricks. Just a killer
  rock band delivering a dynamic\, ALL-LIVE performance every night (with 
