SUMMARY: Butch Cassidy and the Sundance Kid | 5X Series: Robert Redford
DESCRIPTION:Loosely based on the true story of a band of outlaws who elud
 ed the U.S. government after committing train robberies\, Butch Cassidy a
 nd the Sundance Kid stars two of the biggest names of the 1960s\, Paul Ne
 wman and Robert Redford\, as the titular outlaws who must flee to Bolivia
  when the law gets too close. Encapsulating the anti-authoritarian mental
 ity of its era\, this endlessly quotable and offbeat western has been bel
 oved by audiences for decades—and rightfully so. [110 min\; western\, com
 edy\, drama\; English and Spanish]
