SUMMARY: Performance by Visiting Artist Puppies Puppies
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a special intimate performance with visiting mult
 idisciplinary artist Jade Guanaro Kuriki-Olivo (Puppies Puppies) https://
 art21.org/artist/puppies-puppies-jade-guanaro-kuriki-olivo/ .\n\nKuriki-O
 livo is known for her conceptual works of sculpture\, installation\, and 
 performance that combine readymade objects\, popular culture\, and autobi
 ography to address themes of transgender identity\, race\, and power in c
 ontemporary society. Jade's work is currently featured on this month's co
 ver of Art in America https://www.artnews.com/art-in-america/interviews/p
 uppies-puppies-jade-guanaro-kuriki-olivo-cover-dead-liberty-skeleton-1234
 774239/ \, and two of her sculptures were featured in the 2024 Venice htt
 ps://www.labiennale.org/en/art/2024/nucleo-contemporaneo/puppies-puppies-
 jade-guanaro-kuriki-olivo Biennial https://www.labiennale.org/en/art/2024
 /nucleo-contemporaneo/puppies-puppies-jade-guanaro-kuriki-olivo . Her 201
 7 work Liberté (Liberty)\, was the first and only work of performance art
  to be acquired by the Whitney Museum of American Art for its permanent c
 ollection.
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,Free,Live,Media
