SUMMARY: New Exhibitions pARTy at the Brown County Art Guild!
DESCRIPTION:Brown County Art Guild\n\nNew Exhibitions pARTy\n\nGallery Re
 ception Celebrating New Exhibitions!\n\nSaturday March 28\, 2026\n\n2-4 p
 m\n\nStep into a world of vibrant colors and rich textures as we invite y
 ou to the “New Exhibitions pARTy” at the Brown County Art Guild! This cel
 ebration showcases brand new artwork from our talented Guild Artist Membe
 rs\, all inspired by the refreshing beauty of spring. With 2 new captivat
 ing exhibits\, Guild Exhibition & Sale\, Nature’s Symphony – Special Exhi
 bition & Sale our attendees will discover exceptional pieces perfect for 
 art collectors and enthusiasts alike.\n\nWander through our curated galle
 ries enjoying light refreshments & live piano music by Clara Stanley.\n\n
 We are proud to offer this event free of charge\, welcoming visitors to j
 oin us in honoring the incredible artistic talent that thrives at the Gui
 ld.\n\n------------------------------------------------------------------
 -------------------------------\n\nBrown County Art Guild – A not for pro
 fit organization located in the heart of downtown Nashville\, Indiana. On
  display throughout its galleries is a prized collection of historic pain
 tings as well as current works for sale from regional award-winning membe
 r artists. Also offered throughout the year are artist demonstrations\, w
 orkshops\, and special exhibits.\n\nGallery hours March through December 
 2026: Monday – Saturday\, 11 – 5 and Sunday\, 12 – 4\n\nIf you would like
  additional information\, please call 812.988.6185 or view our website ht
 tps://browncountyartguild.org/ https://browncountyartguild.org/
