  following the sneak peek.\n\nWhile there\, enjoy some food and the oppor
 tunity to bid on locally-made and donated auction items. The film is bein
 g produced by Bloomington-based Women with Guts Productions. There will a
 lso be a brief talkback with members of the cast following the screening.
