SUMMARY: The Brown County Art Guild presents Artist is In !
DESCRIPTION:Artist is In\n\nGuild Artist Demonstration Series\n\nDianna P
 orter\n\nSaturday\, April 11\n\n1 -3 pm\n\nJoin us as Dianna demonstrates
  her approach to painting with oils and the creative process she brings t
 o the canvas. Watch as she explores brushstrokes\, layering\, application
  techniques\, and color mixing—revealing what’s possible with this rich a
 nd expressive medium.\n\nAll are welcome\, free\n\n----------------------
 ------------------------------------------------------------------\n\nBro
 wn County Art Guild – A not for profit organization located in the heart 
 of downtown Nashville\, Indiana. On display throughout its galleries is a
  prized collection of historic paintings as well as current works for sal
 e from regional award-winning member artists. Also offered throughout the
  year are artist demonstrations\, workshops\, and special exhibits.\n\nGa
 llery hours March through December 2026\, Monday – Saturday\, 11 – 5 and 
 Sunday\, 12 – 4 or by appointment.\n\nIf you would like more information\
 , call 812.988.6185 or visit our web site https://browncountyartguild.org
 / https://browncountyartguild.org/
CATEGORIES:Nashville,Visual-Arts
