SUMMARY: UpDating
DESCRIPTION:UPDATING is the critically-acclaimed New York City-based live
  dating & comedy show bringing two singles on blindfolded first dates in 
 front of live audiences. Dubbed “the most raw dating show in existence\,”
  what follows is a hilarious show with audience participation\, raw momen
 ts\, and relatable feedback on modern romance in real-time with real peop
 le. Reality TV…unfolding & unedited on stage!\n\nCreated\, Produced\, and
  Hosted by NYC-based comedians\, Brandon Berman (@bermmy16) & Harrison Fo
 rman (@htforman)\n\nHost: Brandon Berman Sidekick: Harrison Forman\nDater
 s: Two Local Singles\n\nFor more information on casting please go to @UPD
