SUMMARY: Spaceballs (1987)
DESCRIPTION:“May the Schwartz be with you” this May 4th with Mel Brooks' 
 1987 cult classic parody of the Star Wars franchise.\n\nIn a distant gala
 xy\, planet Spaceball has depleted its air supply\, leaving its citizens 
 reliant on a product called “Perri-Air.” In desperation\, Spaceball’s lea
 der President Skroob (Mel Brooks) orders the evil Dark Helmet (Rick Moran
 is) to kidnap Princess Vespa (Daphne Zuniga) of oxygen-rich Druidia and h
 old her hostage in exchange for air.\n\nBut help arrives for the Princess
  in the form of renegade space pilot Lone Starr (Bill Pullman) and his ha
 lf-man\, half-dog partner\, Barf (John Candy).\n\nRated: PG\nLength: 1hr 
 36mins\nFormat: DCP
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,Film,In-Person
