SUMMARY: Mamma Mia (2008)
DESCRIPTION:Constellation Stage and Screen & BCT Present:\nMamma Mia! (20
 08)\n\nCalling all dancing queens and super troupers!\nExperience the mag
 ic of ABBA’s greatest hits on the big screen in this feel-good movie musi
 cal about a bride-to-be searching for her real father. Based on the Broad
 way musical of the same name\, Mamma Mia! is a high-energy celebration of
  love\, friendship\, and timeless pop classics.\n\nPre-Show Extravaganza:
 \nBe sure to dress in your Mamma Mia best\, because we’re kicking off the
  screening with a costume contest!\nShow off your disco- and island-inspi
 red looks for the chance to win a fabulous prize. Come early to take phot
 os at our photo booth and grab a themed cocktail from the bar.
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,Film,Tickets,In-Person
