SUMMARY: Making Midwest 2026
DESCRIPTION:Making Midwest 2026 is the gathering that defends creativity 
 in its purest form—through connection\, conversation\, and creation.\n\nT
 his one-day conference features esteemed guest speakers\, exclusive netwo
 rking activities\, and a place where artists\, studios\, and thinkers can
  build the next era of human-made work.\n\nThis is a call to arms for qua
 lity\, for truth\, and for the messy brilliance only people can create.\n
 \nJoin the battle for creativity on June 27th\, 2026 at Columbus College 
 of Art & Design.\n\nTickets available at www.makingmidwest.com/ https://w
 ww.makingmidwest.com/\n\n
CATEGORIES:Columbus,Advocates,Freedom,In-Person
