SUMMARY: Elvis: In Person Starring Matt Stone
DESCRIPTION:The GREATEST ELVIS CONCERT EXPERIENCE IN AMERICA is RETURNING
  to the Buskirk-Chumley Theater on August 21st!\n\nInternationally recogn
 ized by Graceland and the Elvis Presley Estate\, the show’s star\, Matt S
 tone\, performs the CLOSEST THING to the King in history! Matt brings a n
 ever-before-seen level of authenticity and attention to detail to his cra
 ft\, CAPTIVATING audiences with flawless recreation of the King of Rock ’
 n’ Roll in his prime!\n\nHe’s not an “Elvis impersonator\,” but a talente
 d vocalist portraying the GREATEST ENTERTAINER OF ALL TIME in a theatrica
 l production— and after seeing this ELECTRIFYING SPECTACLE\, you’ll remem
 ber ELVIS THE ICON\, and forget the punchline.\n\nHe has earned the appro
 val of Elvis’ friends and family\, who have said:\n\n“When I heard [Matt]
 … now if I close my eyes that’s Elvis! It touched my heart. The only pers
 on I ever heard sing like that was my brother\, and [Matt] was real close
 —SCARY— that’s how close it was.” -Billy Stanley (Elvis’ Step Brother)\n\
 n“Matt is incredibly gifted & handsome\, with incredible energy and sex a
 ppeal.” – Joyce Bova (Longtime Elvis Girlfriend)\n\nHe has even been hear
 d on SiriusXM’s ELVIS RADIO!\n\nBacked by a sensational all-star band\, M
 att Stone MESMERIZES fans into blue-suede bliss as they’re HYPNOTIZED int
 o thinking Elvis is BACK IN THE BUILDING at the PEAK of his prowess!
CATEGORIES:Bloomington,In-Person,Live,Music
